# 15. Problems We Faced

## Problem 1

Grafana CrashLoopBackOff

Reason

Old configuration remained after reinstall.

Solution

Deleted

Helm release

Secrets

ConfigMaps

Reinstalled cleanly.

---

## Problem 2

Loki Installation Failed

Reason

New chart required

Schema Config.

Solution

Used

```text
loki.useTestSchema=true
```

for local environment.

---

## Problem 3

Loki Datasource Failed

Reason

Wrong URL

```text
localhost
```

Correct

```text
http://loki-gateway.default.svc.cluster.local
```

inside Kubernetes

or

```text
http://loki-gateway
```

for cluster communication.

---

## Problem 4

Node Exporter CrashLoopBackOff

Reason

Docker Desktop Kubernetes limitation.

Node Exporter expects host-level Linux filesystem access.

This issue is common in local Docker Desktop clusters and does not affect application monitoring.

---

## Problem 5

Promtail Not Sending Logs

Reason

Wrong Loki endpoint.

Solution

Updated

```text
config.clients[0].url
```

to Loki Gateway.

